	     <br clear=all><small>Posted @ Sat, Aug 24th 8:41 PM 2002</small></td></tr>
	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=100518><span id= >Meirril</span></a><br><span id=notbold>204 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default [1.80]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Compaired to the rest of the idols, I'm starting to think that Karana got the shaft. The good: any worshiper of Karana should be able to get a benifit from all the stats (unless your a warrior. Why would a warrior worship Karana?). The bad: Other idols either offer higher AC, or Stats, or saves. Later in the game, you realy want the saves, or higher stats to make room in other slots for gear with saves. It's a good peice of gear, but not sure it's up to snuff with the rest of the idols. Maybe if it gave a bonus save against fire/cold (say +3? +2?). Ah well.</p>&nbsp;<br>Meirril, Fennin Ro</td></td></tr>
